                    <li>The ten-year tender schedule provides renewable energy developers and investors with the certainty they need</li>
                </ul>',
            imageSrc: '/static/img/what-to-do-2.jpg'
        })
    }}

    {{
        ContentWithImage.render({
            imgPosition: '', 
            categoryTitle: 'The progress we’ve made',
            contentTitle: 'The Roadmap will support the private sector to deliver at least 12 GW of new renewable electricity generation.',
